### TechHive User Management API - Validation Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7154
@token = TechHive2024SecureToken

### 1. Create User - Missing Required Fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John"
}

### 2. Create User - Invalid Email Format
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "role": "Developer"
}

### 3. Create User - Invalid Role
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
